title: Luka Versus KD
description:
Jalen & Jacoby tackle a thriller between the Mavs and the Nets. It was supposed to be Luka vs KD, but the final shot was hit by the man they traded for Porzingis - Spencer Dinwiddie. We break it all down, touch on the Wolves win and the Warriors loss - was Smart's dive dirty? Tune in to find all that, and a whole lot more.
